<title>USA: American Brands seeking debtholder consent.</title>
<headline>American Brands seeking debtholder consent.</headline>
<dateline>OLD GREENWICH, Conn. 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>American Brands Inc said Thursday it was soliciting consents from certain debt holders to amend the indentures governing certain of its U.S. debt securities.</p>
<p>The action is being taken in connection with the spinoff of its U.K.-based Gallaher tobacco business, it said.</p>
<p>The proposed indenture modification would expressly permit the spinoff and related transactions, it said.</p>
<p>The solicitations are being made to all holders of record as of May 8, it said. The solicitation period will begin on May 9 and will expire May 22, unless extended, it said.</p>
